{# Console report template for prioritisation validation #}
{# Input: result (PrioritisationResult), data_file (Path), jira_base_url (str), verbose (bool), team_mappings (Dict), team_managers (Dict) #}
{% set has_conflicts = result.priority_conflicts|length > 0 %}
{% set has_missing = result.missing_commitments|length > 0 %}
{% set has_quality_issues = result.data_quality_issues|length > 0 %}
{% set has_unlisted = result.unlisted_initiatives|length > 0 %}

================================================================================
Initiative Priority Validation Report
================================================================================
Data Source: {{ data_file }}
Total Initiatives: {{ result.metadata.total_initiatives }}
Active (non-Done/Cancelled): {{ result.metadata.active_initiatives }}
Configured in Priorities: {{ result.metadata.priorities_count }}
Validated (non-Discovery, in config): {{ result.metadata.validated_initiatives }}
Teams Analyzed: {{ result.metadata.teams_analyzed }}

{% if result.metadata.missing_from_data %}
⚠️  Warning: {{ result.metadata.missing_from_data|length }} initiatives in priority config not found in quarter data:
{% for key in result.metadata.missing_from_data %}
   - {{ key }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if has_unlisted %}
⚠️  Warning: {{ result.unlisted_initiatives|length }} prioritised initiatives not in priority config:
{% for init in result.unlisted_initiatives %}
   - {{ init.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ init.key) }}: {{ init.summary }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if has_quality_issues %}

⚠️  Data Quality Issues
================================================================================
{{ result.data_quality_issues|length }} initiatives missing teams_involved field:

{% for init in result.data_quality_issues %}
{{ init.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ init.key) }}: {{ init.summary }}
   Status: {{ init.status }}
   ⚠️  Missing teams_involved - cannot validate team commitments

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{# Section 1: Priority Conflicts #}
{% if has_conflicts %}

⚠️  Section 1: Priority Conflicts
================================================================================
{{ result.priority_conflicts|length }} teams committed to lower-priority initiatives while skipping higher-priority ones:

{% for conflict in result.priority_conflicts %}
{{ conflict.team_display }} ({{ conflict.team_key }})
   Committed to:
{% for init in conflict.committed_to %}
      - Priority #{{ init.priority }}: {{ init.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ init.key) }} - {{ init.title }}
{% endfor %}

   Missing higher priorities:
{% for init in conflict.missing_higher_priorities %}
      - Priority #{{ init.priority }}: {{ init.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ init.key) }} - {{ init.title }}
{% endfor %}

{% endfor %}
{% else %}

✅ Section 1: Priority Conflicts
================================================================================
No priority conflicts detected. All teams committing to prioritised initiatives are respecting priority order.
{% endif %}

{# Section 2: Missing Commitments #}
{% if has_missing %}

⚠️  Section 2: Missing Commitments
================================================================================
{{ result.missing_commitments|length }} teams expected to contribute but not committed:

{% for missing in result.missing_commitments %}
{{ missing.team_display }} ({{ missing.team_key }})
{% for issue in missing.issues %}
   {% if issue.reason == 'no_epic' %}
   ❌ {{ issue.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.key) }}: {{ issue.title }}
      → No epic created
   {% elif issue.reason == 'missing_rag' %}
   ⚠️  {{ issue.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.key) }}: {{ issue.title }}
      → Epic {{ issue.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.epic_key) }} exists but has no RAG status
   {% elif issue.reason == 'red_rag' %}
   🔴 {{ issue.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.key) }}: {{ issue.title }}
      → Epic {{ issue.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.epic_key) }} has RED RAG (blocked/at risk)
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% endfor %}
{% else %}

✅ Section 2: Missing Commitments
================================================================================
All expected teams have at least one green/yellow epic commitment.
{% endif %}

{# Section 3: Initiative Health Dashboard #}

📊 Section 3: Initiative Health Dashboard
================================================================================
Initiative-centric view of team commitments (in priority order):

{% for init in result.initiative_health %}
Priority #{{ init.priority }}: {{ init.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ init.key) }}
   {{ init.title }}
   Expected teams ({{ init.expected_teams|length }}): {{ init.expected_teams|join(', ') }}
{% if init.completed_teams %}
   ✅ Completed ({{ init.completed_teams|length }}):
{% for team_data in init.completed_teams %}
      - {{ team_data.team }} (Done)
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if init.active_teams %}
   🚧 Active ({{ init.active_teams|length }}):
{% for team_data in init.active_teams %}
      - {{ team_data.team }} ({{ team_data.rag_statuses|join(', ') }})
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if not init.completed_teams and not init.active_teams %}
   ❌ No committed teams
{% endif %}
{% if init.missing_teams %}
   ⚠️  Missing ({{ init.missing_teams|length }}):
{% for missing in init.missing_teams %}
   {% if missing.reason == 'no_epic' %}
      - {{ missing.team }} → No epic created
   {% elif missing.reason == 'missing_rag' %}
      - {{ missing.team }} → Epic {{ missing.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ missing.epic_key) }} needs RAG status
   {% elif missing.reason == 'red_rag' %}
      - {{ missing.team }} → Epic {{ missing.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ missing.epic_key) }} has RED RAG
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

{# Section 4: Action Items for Managers #}
{# Check if there are any actions needed #}
{% set ns = namespace(has_initiative_gaps=false) %}
{% for init in result.initiative_health %}
   {% if init.missing_teams %}
      {% set ns.has_initiative_gaps = true %}
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if has_conflicts or has_missing or ns.has_initiative_gaps %}

📋 Section 4: Action Items for Managers
================================================================================
Action items grouped by responsible team:

{# Extract and group actions by team #}
{% set teams_with_actions = [] %}
{% for conflict in result.priority_conflicts %}
   {% if conflict.team_display not in teams_with_actions %}
      {% set _ = teams_with_actions.append(conflict.team_display) %}
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% for missing in result.missing_commitments %}
   {% if missing.team_display not in teams_with_actions %}
      {% set _ = teams_with_actions.append(missing.team_display) %}
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{# Also include teams with missing initiatives #}
{% for init in result.initiative_health %}
   {% for missing_team in init.missing_teams %}
      {% if missing_team.team not in teams_with_actions %}
         {% set _ = teams_with_actions.append(missing_team.team) %}
      {% endif %}
   {% endfor %}
{% endfor %}

{% for team_display in teams_with_actions|sort %}
{# Find actions for this team #}
{% set team_conflicts = [] %}
{% set team_missing = [] %}
{% set team_initiative_gaps = [] %}
{% for conflict in result.priority_conflicts %}
   {% if conflict.team_display == team_display %}
      {% set _ = team_conflicts.append(conflict) %}
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% for missing in result.missing_commitments %}
   {% if missing.team_display == team_display %}
      {% set _ = team_missing.append(missing) %}
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{# Find missing initiatives for this team #}
{% for init in result.initiative_health %}
   {% for missing_team in init.missing_teams %}
      {% if missing_team.team == team_display %}
         {% set _ = team_initiative_gaps.append({'init_key': init.key, 'init_title': init.title, 'reason': missing_team.reason, 'epic_key': missing_team.epic_key}) %}
      {% endif %}
   {% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{# Get manager info for this team #}
{% set team_key = team_mappings.get(team_display, team_display) %}
{% set manager_info = team_managers.get(team_key, {}) %}
{% set manager_tag = manager_info.get('notion_handle', '') %}
{% set manager_suffix = ' ' + manager_tag if manager_tag else '' %}

{{ team_display }}{{ manager_suffix }}:
{% for conflict in team_conflicts %}
{% for init in conflict.missing_higher_priorities %}
   [ ] Review commitment to priority #{{ init.priority }} ({{ init.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ init.key) }}) vs lower priorities
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{% for missing in team_missing %}
{% for issue in missing.issues %}
   {% if issue.reason == 'no_epic' %}
   [ ] Create epic for {{ issue.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.key) }} ({{ issue.title }})
   {% elif issue.reason == 'missing_rag' %}
   [ ] Set RAG status for {{ issue.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.epic_key) }} in {{ issue.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.key) }}
   {% elif issue.reason == 'red_rag' %}
   [ ] Resolve blocker for {{ issue.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.epic_key) }} in {{ issue.key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ issue.key) }} or deprioritize
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{# Add initiative-specific gaps #}
{% for gap in team_initiative_gaps %}
   {% if gap.reason == 'no_epic' %}
   [ ] Create epic for {{ gap.init_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ gap.init_key) }} ({{ gap.init_title }})
   {% elif gap.reason == 'missing_rag' %}
   [ ] Set RAG status for {{ gap.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ gap.epic_key) }} in {{ gap.init_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ gap.init_key) }}
   {% elif gap.reason == 'red_rag' %}
   [ ] Resolve blocker for {{ gap.epic_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ gap.epic_key) }} in {{ gap.init_key|hyperlink(jira_base_url ~ '/browse/' ~ gap.init_key) }} or deprioritize
   {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% endfor %}
{% else %}

✅ Section 4: Action Items for Managers
================================================================================
No action items - all teams respecting priorities and commitments.
{% endif %}

================================================================================
Summary
================================================================================
{% if has_conflicts or has_missing %}
⚠️  Validation found {{ result.priority_conflicts|length }} priority conflicts and {{ result.missing_commitments|length }} missing commitments.

Review action items above and work with team managers to address gaps.
{% else %}
✅ All teams respecting prioritised initiative priorities and commitments.
{% endif %}

Exit code: {% if has_conflicts or has_missing %}1 (issues found){% else %}0 (success){% endif %}
